{
  "$comment": [
    "Data-driven annotation spec for the tutorial screenshot pipeline.",
    "Each entry maps a scene-id to a list of regions overlaid on its screenshot.",
    "",
    "Region fields:",
    "  selector  CSS / data-testid selector resolved at runtime by Playwright.",
    "            The pipeline reads boundingBox() and overlays the region.",
    "            Use `{ selector: \"...\", inset: { x, y, w, h } }` to nudge.",
    "  xy        Absolute viewport coordinates `{x,y,w,h}` (for pill / overlay",
    "            anchors that have no DOM hook — e.g. the Causa launcher pill).",
    "  label     Caption text painted next to the region.",
    "  colour    Hex stroke + label background (default `#e53935` red).",
    "  arrow     Optional `{from: {x,y}, to: {x,y}}` SVG arrow overlay.",
    "  labelPos  `above` | `below` | `right` | `left` (auto-flips near edges).",
    "",
    "Annotation rendering target: SVG overlay injected pre-screenshot, torn",
    "down after. Crisp anti-aliased strokes, drop-shadowed labels."
  ],

  "causa-floating-pill": [
    {
      "xy": { "x": 1150, "y": 730, "w": 110, "h": 50 },
      "colour": "#1976d2",
      "label": "Ctrl+Shift+C  -> open Causa",
      "labelPos": "above"
    }
  ],

  "causa-shell-opened": [
    {
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"rf-causa-shell\"]",
      "inset": { "y": 0, "h": 28 },
      "colour": "#43a047",
      "label": "Causa shell — overlays the live app",
      "labelPos": "below"
    }
  ],

  "causa-sidebar-panels": [
    {
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"rf-causa-sidebar-item-event-detail\"]",
      "groupExtendTo": "[data-testid=\"rf-causa-sidebar-item-copilot\"]",
      "colour": "#fb8c00",
      "label": "16 panels - three bands",
      "labelPos": "right"
    }
  ],

  "causa-event-detail": [
    {
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"rf-causa-event-detail\"]",
      "inset": { "y": 4, "h": 48 },
      "colour": "#43a047",
      "label": "Event vector + diff + cascade",
      "labelPos": "below"
    }
  ],

  "causa-time-travel": [
